{
  "stem": "15197.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I talk about him constantly and not mention the name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Benjamin [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in the States he remained Benjamin, but from [POLISH] he became Meed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said with such a name it would be very difficult in the States to pronounce the name.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he's Benjamin Meed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Benjamin was involved in the underground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His particular task was to prepare hiding places for Jews, to make double walls and the Jews can hide under or to make some hiding places where illegal material-- pamphlets or papers-- you can hide.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was involved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He also was involved with finding for children places where to hide.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was involved in his own way, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not possible in a normal way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have to smuggle them out only when we had a place where to put them, to hide.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was much easier with girls than with little boys because little boys were circumcised and little girls can always be as a Polish girl.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were certain points at the wall of the ghetto where we were able to bribe the police, but they were smuggled-- went on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was not easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes I know a friend of ours, we worked together in the underground and he was later the so-called engineer and made the primitive Molotov cocktails and organized in the ghetto the primitive factory of ammunition.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Mikhail [POLISH], they smuggled out their 10-month-old daughter and they left the child at the steps of a church and he went away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he told me waiting to see what happened with this bundle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And somebody heard crying and they knocked at the church door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they came-- somebody came out and took the baby in, so he knew that the baby is there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Children were smugglers.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
